051  //@DefaultFor({ "mybal" })
052  @Subcommand({ "balmenu", "menu", "mybal" })
053  @Usage("Money.MyBal.Arguments")
054  @Description("Money.MyBal.Description")
055  @CommandPermission("tne.money.mybal")
056  public void onMyBal(final BukkitCommandActor sender) {
057
058    net.tnemc.core.command.MoneyCommand.onMyBal(new PaperCMDSource(sender));
059  }
060
061  @Subcommand({ "help", "?" })
062  @Usage("Help.Arguments")
063  @Description("Help.Description")
064  public void help(final BukkitCommandActor actor, final Help.RelatedCommands<?> commands, @Default("1") final int page) {
065
066    BaseCommand.help(new PaperCMDSource(actor), commands, page);
067  }

069  //@DefaultFor({ "bal", "money", "eco", "balance" })
070  @Subcommand({ "balance", "bal", "val" })
071  @Usage("Money.Balance.Arguments")
072  @Description("Money.Balance.Description")
073  @CommandPermission("tne.money.balance")
074  public void onBalance(final BukkitCommandActor sender, @Default("") @Named("currency") final Currency currency, @Default(DEFAULT_WORLD) @Named("region") final String region) {
075
076    System.out.println("Currency: " + currency);
077
078    if(currency == null) {
079      System.out.println("Currency is null");
080    }
081
082    net.tnemc.core.command.MoneyCommand.onBalance(new PaperCMDSource(sender), currency, region);
083  }
